  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDViYmE0ZWM4NTkyOTBkNTdlOWNiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMTcwJmhlaWdodD0xNTU4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/45bba4ec859290d57e9cb.jpg?width=1170&amp;height=1558\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/45bba4ec859290d57e9cb.jpg?width=1170&amp;height=1558\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/45bba4ec859290d57e9cb.jpg?width=1170&amp;height=1558\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n天不怕地不怕，爾最怕我最怕，鐮刀與槌子<br/>\r\n遇到鐮刀財清光，遇到鎚子十年牢。<br/>\r\n當時只是隨便一個玩笑，和《古惑仔》中，「B仔，你仲惡過共產黨」差不多。在再版也保留下來，但今天…<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDFmNmRjNmMzYjQzZjgxNWMwNzUzLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDQyJmhlaWdodD0xNDUw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1f6dc6c3b43f815c0753.jpg?width=1042&amp;height=1450\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1f6dc6c3b43f815c0753.jpg?width=1042&amp;height=1450\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d1f6dc6c3b43f815c0753.jpg?width=1042&amp;height=1450\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
